descriptionHtml:
Since my last description was a bit skinny, let me make a new one..
This is a showcase mode, there is no gameplay here, just some exteriors, what im working on is a mod to remake Esterior, to be more precise Black Harbor, the capital. I will be uploading new material weekly, to show some updates, but now im just working on exterior, and ive got some of it done, like i said, any help would be appreciated, quest wise, idea wise, or modding wise.

The entrance is in Riverwood, just a door in the city, need somewhere to put it! :D

Thanks :D

Update Started working on it again, added a couple of things,just do the tcl command, i havent added any doors yet since i remodled the walls and towers.
